-- General --

Pointcache Tool
Version: 	0.1b
Date:		01/11/2014
Contact:	onectin@onectin.fr
Licence: 	Gnu GPLv3


-- Installation --

1. Put the "pointCacheTool" folder in your default script directory.
(In 3dsMax, see "Customize > Configure System Path > Additional Scripts" to know that directory.)
2. Execute "pointcacheTool.ms" in 3dsMax
3. Set the preferences
4. Restart 3dsMax

-- Usage --

- Simply execute "pointcacheTool.ms"
- You can find pointcacheTool in the UI category "#Onectin"
More informations: www.onectin.fr/pointcache-tool